HX-2026-04-10:
Fri Apr 10 09:33:43 PM EDT 2026
xinterp-2026-04-10:
This interpreter was implemented in ATS2.
And the primary implementation work was done in 2022
(and some in 2023).
It did serve well its purpose of testing various ATS3 designs made
at the very beginning of the ATS3 development. In particular, it
helped tremedously to clarify the semantics of templates. For
instance, it gave a reference implementation for template resolution,
that is, resolving the issue of locating the template implementation
for each template use.
